components.name: LoginFormComponent
components.templateData:
<form [formGroup]="loginForm" class="login-form-container">
  <app-input
    label="Email"
    placeholder="Digite seu email"
    width="100%"
    formControlName="email"
  ></app-input>
  <app-input
    label="Senha"
    placeholder="Digite sua senha"
    width="100%"
    type="password"
    formControlName="password"
  ></app-input>
  <app-button
    width="100%"
    (onClick)="login()"
  >
    Entrar
  </app-button>
</form>
